"佢有日喊緊打畀我，同我講<br />\n我真係頂唔順，我承受唔到第二次，我覺得我今次捱唔到。<br />\n（佢同ex拍5年分咗一年，一直想復合，然後復合一日又飛咗我frd揀咗第條仔）<br />\n講真食飯出嚟玩啲錢，我又唔係真係好想貪，只係有人請何樂不為嘅心態。<br />\n但佢咁樣有自殺前科，我係真心信佢會死多次。"},{"pid":"ea444368d2980478885e41e50b19f4b7bd0fae9f","tid":935543,"uid":154783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1b15c550fce38e65476c4330b58554ff85ec134","tid":935543,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"193602bc25e534be8fc71e80ee2f4c8f200d6930","tid":935543,"uid":154783,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"quote":{"pid":"aada3e85bc9a4cc2c1da5dfc49b3b69add4defbc","tid":935543,"uid":177089,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T06:05:28.000Z","msg":"攬乜撚野啊八婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw佢比較有錢，<br />\n所以佢都好錫我<br />\n因果關係？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T06:08:10.000Z","msg":"咁平時我地個圈子就係，大家邊個贏波/出糧就出大份。<br />\n出嚟食飯邊個手緊就唔洗畀。<br />\n咁我長期手緊，平時啲朋友都會叫我夾細份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T06:09:29.000Z","msg":"咁同佢有錢所以好錫你有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你話佢因為你無錢主動想俾多啲/請埋你就話姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T06:15:17.000Z","msg":"講得唔清楚，<br />\n其實佢對個個都好，係好錫大家至啱。<br />\n不過係特別就我咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac6bcf1c2075f4bb626118ecb3cff4b0c958359","tid":935543,"uid":154783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"634e244646bb5f314234a3828e53c67fd993f443","tid":935543,"uid":107172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T06:09:15.000Z","msg":"你當佢係咩？拿拿聲同佢講清楚啦，一陣真係唔知佢會做d 乜，隨時自殺俾你睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T06:15:48.000Z","msg":"有無睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講咗好多次"},{"pid":"45d7773065ac2aa151ad436d40ae40d63783086c","tid":935543,"uid":154783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":