owerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> GAY"},{"pid":"32bda3d25b1a869513a4276b8fdcb0aa6a6236c9","tid":935543,"uid":9964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T06:36:57.000Z","msg":"friend hug<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a6450d428e510438d67ab22850f58061cb09237","tid":935543,"uid":181905,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T06:43:17.000Z","msg":"是咁的，講講背景。<br />\n我半年前返工識咗個男仔好啱傾。（熟客）<br />\n後尾因為佢話可以教我功課所以一直都有keep contact，<br />\n佢因為ex嘅事放棄晒原本啲圈子，得返返工哩班。<br />\n<br />\n因為我同佢啱傾，同埋佢比較有錢，<br />\n所以佢都好錫我，成日送返屋企<span style=\"color: red;\">又俾錢</span>又隨傳隨到咁。<br />\n直到有日我同事突然話，乜你唔覺得佢鍾意你㗎咩，<br />\n我就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，因為佢對個個都好好，我就無咩為意。<br />\n跟住我就同佢挑開嚟講，<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實你知我唔會同你一齊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我知啊。你要啲高大靚仔，我哩啲，自己知自己事啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 況且愈同你傾得多計，我就愈知道我地根本係兩個世界嘅人<br />\n咁我就當佢已經明解啦，就唔再提。<br />\n<br />\n早排佢因為佢ex啲嘢好撚唔開心，喺舖頭到喊，<br />\n我同事就打電話叫我飛的出嚟幫拖。<br />\n去到大家嘻嘻哈哈咗好耐，<br />\n之後我叫佢出去陪我買啲嘢咁，<br />\n全程我都無講正經嘢，佢又唔出聲淨係眼濕濕咁。<br />\n我見佢咁就伸開手諗住攬下佢，有個friendly hug咁。<br />\n佢就攬住我喊咗陣，然後就返去。<br />\n<br />\n自從嗰日攬完之後，佢對我加幾倍咁好，<br />\n有啲咩機會掂到我隻手就捉實，<br />\n又或者係成日搭車/坐低都瞓瞓下挨落嚟。<br />\n我就好撚驚，好驚佢依賴我，<br />\n因為佢有情緒病，啲情緒嚟得好快，又自殺過（早排嘅事嚟）<br />\n加上我都要人教我功課，<br />\n變相我在情在理都唔可以就咁斬纜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且同佢係真係好傾，直頭算係知己，唔想就咁無咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我一有機會就已經不停同佢講我唔會揀佢，<br />\n仲數晒啲原因畀佢聽，佢聽到好撚hurt。<br />\n屌我真係唔知點先可以令佢死心，<br />\n而家我地成班人出嚟玩，我都好刻意同返佢AA，亦都唔會俾佢送。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌，真係好撚煩，唉，點解要逼我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你做雞?"},{"pid":"3b8c63a5481d3905e8a60b12ca4592a4a9c9cfb0","tid":935543,"uid":154783,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e6f56c46ed395048e056092e10f6f4661fff4223","tid":935543,"uid":108690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6048cae3151622f94768385e734a8cb49e4ef935","tid":935543,"uid":154783,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"ef3db50f8853ac7769c155629976b9ccfc95b576","tid":935543,"uid":205884,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T06:18:21.000Z","msg":"你根本就係自私 <br />\n想有人錫 又唔想自己有責任"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T06:21:48.000Z","msg":"係，我知，我同個個追我嘅男仔都係咁講。<br />\n正常追我啲人一表白我就會斬纜，<br />\n但哩個我真係唔太想斬，亦唔識斬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nThat&rsquo;s why佢話同我係兩個世界嘅人。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T06:25:00.000Z","msg":"點解唔想斬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T06:56:23.000Z","msg":"第一 同佢啱傾 對於我嚟講係好珍貴嘅事<br />\n第二 佢嚴重抑鬱 佢而家咁依賴我 我唔放心掉低佢<br />\n<br />\n我真係無男女之情嘅諗法而佢亦清楚明白"},{"pid":"6ad8a281b872df668637f0b8b54616dc4ef6d821","tid":935543,"uid":154783,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d1191512dd0672ebdb8832a30915c98a41969874","tid":935543,"uid":13288,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"e6f56c46